Package Server.RequestHanlders

  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    AddBuyOrder
    Handle request to add a buy order to the market
    AddSellOrder
    Handle request to add a sell order to the market
    AssignCredits
    Handle request to assign credits to an organisation Only users with admin permissions can use
    ChangePassword
    Handle request to change a users password by editing the database
    CreateAsset
    Handle request to create an asset
    CreateOrganisation
    Handle request to create an organisation Only users with admin permissions can use
    DeleteAsset
    Handle request to delete an asset Only users with admin permissions can use
    DeleteOrder
    Handle request to delete a buy or sell order from the market
    DeleteOrganisation
    Handle request to delete an organisation Only users with admin permissions can use
    DeleteUser
    Handle request to delete a user from the database
    GetAllListings
    Handle request to get all listings on the database To be called by GUI when viewing market
    GetFilteredListings
    Handle request to get listings with certain filters To be called by GUI when viewing market, should be flexible to return appropriate results based on filters chosen
    GetSearchListings
    Handle request to get listings matching a string To be called by GUI when viewing market, should be flexible to return appropriate results based on the string searched
    Login
    Handle Login request on server side
    Logout
    Handle Logout request on server side
    RegisterUser
    Handle request to register a new user
    TransferAssets
    Handle request to transfer assets from one organisation to another Will be called when a sale is made
    TransferCredits
    Handle request to transfer credits from one organisation to another Will be called when a sale is made
